features: Built to Last: The reinforced BAGSMART Workout Bag is designed to withstand the demands of your gym sessions, It is made of high-density durable polyester cloth materials. Premium zippers ensure durability and smooth operation, while the reinforced stitching on the grip handles and padded shoulder strap prevents tearing. Use the duffle bag for a trip to the gym or away for the weekend. We've got you covered.

Large-capacity Sports Bag: Dimensions: 20.86" L x 9.84" W x 10.2" H. The BAGSMART Gym Bag is ideal for everyday use before and after training. The roomy main compartment provides plenty of space for all your fitness equipment and the exterior handy pocket allows easy access to your essentials.

Dry and Wet Separation: Say goodbye to mixing damp and malodorous items with clean ones. The women gym bag features a distinctive wet and dry separation design, preventing your sweaty clothes or wet towels from compromising the cleanliness of your other belongings. Enjoy the peace of mind that comes with keeping hygiene intact, regardless of the intensity of your workout.

Convenient Shoe Compartment: No more worry about shoes taking up valuable space or staining your other items. The gym duffle bag incorporates a separate compartment dedicated solely to footwear, offering ample room for your sneakers or workout shoes. Besides maintaining cleanliness and orderliness, this compartment allows for proper ventilation, effectively eliminating unwanted odors.

Multi-purpose Tote Bag: The versatile gym bag is designed to cater to a wide range of indoor and outdoor activities. It can seamlessly transition from a dry-n-wet separation bag to a gym bag, dance bag, luggage bag, beach bag, cheer bag, mommy bag, hospital bag, nurse bag, overnight bag, and weekender bag. Its adaptability makes it the ideal companion for excursions, travel, and air travel.

After-sales Service: Here at BAGSMART, we strive to deliver the highest-quality product we can to our customers. If there are any quality problems, please do not have any hesitate. We are happy to offer an unconditional refund or replacement. Contact us for a timely and satisfactory answer!

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Tremendous Organizing Duffel Bag
reviews.reviewText: I think this bag is a very phenomenal product for its size.I think its pockets are tremendously helpful. I didn't expect as many pockets as it had, but it allowed me to have different things stored in different compartments, while still having enough space for me to store more work-out tools that I use.I also think the straps that it had helped me carry it in a more convenient manner that I didn't even consider when I was looking for a new duffel bag.Overall, this bag gave me everything I wanted and more, and it allows me to keep most of my things in different pockets for the most part and find them more easily.
